systemData.Description: The system meta data relating to this resource

location.Description: The geo-location where the resource lives

provisioningState.Description: Gets the status of the account at the time the operation was called

createdBy.Description: The identity that created the resource.

createdByType.Description: The type of identity that created the resource.

lastModifiedBy.Description: The identity that last modified the resource.

lastModifiedByType.Description: The type of identity that last modified the resource.

lastModifiedAt.Description: The timestamp of resource last modification (UTC)

provisioningState.Description: Gets the status of the data pool at the time the operation was called

locations.Description: Gets or sets the collection of locations where Data Pool resources should be created

systemData.Description: The system meta data relating to this resource

encryption.Description: Encryption properties of a Data Pool location

keyVaultUri.Description: The URI of a soft delete-enabled Key Vault that is in the same location as the Data Pool location

keyName.Description: The name of Key Vault key

keyVersion.Description: The version of Key Vault key

userAssignedIdentity.Description: The resource ID of a user-assigned Managed Identity used to access the encryption key in the Key Vault. Requires access to the key operations get, wrap, unwrap, and recover
